The Scotts Company




The Scotts Miracle-Gro Company is the world's largest marketer of branded consumer lawn and garden products, with a full range of products for professional horticulture as well. Its products include consumer fertilizers, plant foods, soils and mulches, spreaders, pest controls, grass seed and bird food.  The Temecula Operations facility serves as Scotts' national manufacturing and distribution center for plastic products used to apply lawn care products.








